coolquotes.quote: Don't ever think I fell for you, or fell over you. I didn't fall in love, I rose in it.
coolquotes.author: Toni Morrison

coolquotes.quote: Enthusiam makes up for a host of difficulties.
coolquotes.author: Barack Obama

coolquotes.quote: Open your eyes and see what you can with them before they close forever.
coolquotes.author: Anthony Doerr

coolquotes.quote: Life starts out with everyone clapping when you take a poo and goes downhill from there.
coolquotes.author: Sloane Crosley

coolquotes.quote: Tell me, what is it you plan to do with your one wild and precious life?
coolquotes.author: Mary Oliver
